 alienation in the story.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aJewszRussiavFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aSherman, Joseph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSherman, Joseph, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831105379940 cprintz978030011067840uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030015496240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300154962423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300154962/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY